          "_name": "features11",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features10\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <!---->\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"2\" max=\"6\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitleCard\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Transparent\" name=\"transparentCard\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#fafafa\" condition=\"!transparentCard\">\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardsAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">4</option>\n            <option value=\"5\">5</option>\n            <option value=\"6\">6</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid' : fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"title\">\n            <h3 mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Вхождение в литературу</b></h3>\n            <h4 mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                Subtitle\n            </h4>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/6-288x341.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"top-line\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Camera</b></h4>\n                                        <p class=\"cost mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".cost\">Увлечение творчеством</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">Свое первое произведение — стихотворение — он написал в возрасте 15–16 лет на русском языке (в то время в школе учились на русском).\n<br>В 1923 году он приезжает в Якутск и учится в 7 классе. В то время люди и молодежь писали стихи, приветствуя первый прилет в Якутск летающего судна — самолета. Суорун Омоллоон тоже пишет свое первое стихотворение на якутском языке под названием «Летающее судно» (Көтөр аал), которое было опубликовано в школьном рукописном журнале.&nbsp;</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>1\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/7-246x347.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"top-line\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Mug</b></h4>\n                                        <p class=\"cost mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".cost\">Вхождение в литературу</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">Суорун Омоллоон вошел в якутскую литературу в 1926 году с рассказом «Река Лена» (Өлүөнэ өрүс), напечатанным в журнала «Чолбон». В нем дано великолепное описание завораживающей красоты р. Лены, в которой видны истоки патриотического, глубоко национального начала. Этот рассказ он подписал псевдонимом Т.Уо. — Тыа Уола.\n<br>Через год выступил на страницах того же журнала с рассказами «Анчык», «Охоноон» и др. Они сразу же привлекли внимание новизной содержания, яркостью языка, глубиной художественного обобщения.&nbsp;</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>2\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"../_images/products/product3.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"top-line\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Coffee</b></h4>\n                                        <p class=\"cost mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".cost\">\n                                            $49</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                                            Themes in the Mobirise website builder offer multiple blocks: intros,\n                                            sliders, galleries, forms, articles, and so on. Start a project and click on\n                                            the red plus buttons to see the blocks available for your theme.\n                                        </p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>3\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"../_images/products/product4.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"top-line\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Glasses</b></h4>\n                                        <p class=\"cost mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".cost\">\n                                            $49</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                                            Themes in the Mobirise website builder offer multiple blocks: intros,\n                                            sliders, galleries, forms, articles, and so on. Start a project and click on\n                                            the red plus buttons to see the blocks available for your theme.\n                                        </p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>4\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"../_images/products/product5.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"top-line\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Pineapple</b></h4>\n                                        <p class=\"cost mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".cost\">\n                                            $49\n                                        </p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                                            Themes in the Mobirise website builder offer multiple blocks: intros,\n                                            sliders, galleries, forms, articles, and so on. Start a project and click on\n                                            the red plus buttons to see the blocks available for your theme.\n                                        </p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardsAmount>5\">\n            <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                            <img src=\"../_images/products/product6.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                        <div class=\"card-box\">\n                            <div class=\"row\">\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"top-line\">\n                                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><b>Cat</b></h4>\n                                        <p class=\"cost mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".cost\">\n                                            $49</p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                                <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-10' : fullWidth}\">\n                                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style m-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                                            Themes in the Mobirise website builder offer multiple blocks: intros,\n                                            sliders, galleries, forms, articles, and so on. Start a project and click on\n                                            the red plus buttons to see the blocks available for your theme.\n                                        </p>\n                                    </div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
